<h4 id="_111-二叉树的最小深度" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_111-二叉树的最小深度" aria-hidden="true">#</a> <a href="https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/minimum-depth-of-binary-tree/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">111. 二叉树的最小深度<ExternalLinkIcon/></a></h4>
